  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为HealthTech系统画一个看板，核心是DiagnosticEngine，它要驱动两个主要模块：LabAnalyzer和HIPAA_Vault。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine",
        "HealthTech_LabAnalyzer",
        "HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，DiagnosticEngine作为顶层节点。那LabAnalyzer和HIPAA_Vault是直接挂在这个引擎下面，还是HIPAA_Vault需要独立出来作为一个并行的泳道？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine",
        "HealthTech_LabAnalyzer",
        "HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "HIPAA_Vault比较特殊，它既要被DiagnosticEngine调用，又要反过来给DiagnosticEngine提供合规数据。所以我想让它同时出现在两个位置：一个作为DiagnosticEngine的子任务，另一个作为独立的合规节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault",
        "HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先搭建结构：DiagnosticEngine作为id1，下面挂LabAnalyzer和HIPAA_Vault。然后单独放一个HIPAA_Vault作为id2，让它指向DiagnosticEngine。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "id1",
        "id2",
        "docs",
        "blog",
        "id6"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，LabAnalyzer用docs标识，HIPAA_Vault用blog标识。等等，你刚才说id2指向DiagnosticEngine，这个箭头方向确认一下——是HIPAA_Vault给DiagnosticEngine回传数据对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "id2",
        "id6",
        "blog"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，id2下面的id6就是DiagnosticEngine，表示HIPAA_Vault向它输出。这样id1驱动docs和blog，id2又通过id6反哺id1，形成闭环。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "id1",
        "id2",
        "docs",
        "blog",
        "id6"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "id6和id1都是DiagnosticEngine，会不会让人误解成两个不同的引擎？需要标注清楚它们是同一个实例吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "id1",
        "id6",
        "HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "看板的特性是允许这种跨列引用，我们可以保持名称一致，通过标签隐含它们是同一组件。如果强调实例唯一性，反而破坏了看板的流程视角。您看这样处理可以吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "id1",
        "id6"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "可以，名称一致就够了。另外检查一下：docs和blog作为子项，层级关系有没有问题？LabAnalyzer和HIPAA_Vault应该是平级的。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "docs",
        "blog",
        "id1"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "确认了，docs和blog都直接挂在id1下面，没有嵌套关系。结构是：id1展开两个子项docs和blog，同时id2独立成列，下面挂id6指回DiagnosticEngine。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "id1",
        "docs",
        "blog",
        "id2",
        "id6"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "稍等，我刚才说错了——HIPAA_Vault在id1下面应该用blog，但id2本身也是HIPAA_Vault，这个重复命名会不会在渲染时冲突？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "blog",
        "id2",
        "HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "不会冲突，blog是id1的子项标签，id2是独立节点的标识符，它们可以显示相同的中文名称HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault。看板里这种跨列的同名组件很常见，表示同一服务在不同阶段的状态。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "blog",
        "id2"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "明白了，那就定稿。最终结构：DiagnosticEngine统领LabAnalyzer和HIPAA_Vault，同时HIPAA_Vault作为独立合规节点反向支撑DiagnosticEngine。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine",
        "HealthTech_LabAnalyzer",
        "HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
